LEARN

Usage: ^gLEARN <spell>^n

In order to learn a spell, you need three things.  First, your magical rating
must be above 0.  Second, you must have a spell formula.  Third, you must
have a number of ^Wkarma^n points equal to the force of the desired spell.

^c< 10P 10M > learn tactical nuke^n

^WSee Also: CAST, CREATE, MAGIC, SPELLS, KARMA^n

